question: What is the name of the administrative center of Cēsu novads (Cēsis county) in Latvia?
asked_question_translated: What is the name of the administrative center of Cēsu novads (Cēsis county) in Latvia?
answer: The administrative center of Cēsu novads in Latvia is the town of Cēsis.
